    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cylinder desks, that is writing desks with a cover that rolls up into the desk top, that are designed for ladies; they are distinguished by often having a relatively delicate design and a wide space to accommodate ladies' skirts.</Note_Text>
